===Etymology 1===
Origin uncertain.
====Noun====
{{en-noun|-}}
# {{lb|en|disease}} A [[contagious]] [[tropical disease]], caused by the [[spirochete]] {{taxlink|Treponema pertenue|species}}, characterized by yellowish or reddish [[tumor]]s, which often resemble berries.
#* '''1997''', {{w|Roy Porter}}, ''The Greatest Benefit to Mankind'', Folio Society 2016, p. 16:
#*: Other threats came from organisms co-evolving with humans, including tapeworms and such spirochaetes as ''Treponema'', the agent of syphilis, and the similar skin infection, '''yaws'''.
